question: What restaurant is available in the direction of Baylor Scott And White Institute For Rehabilitation - Lakeway, Lakeway, TX within 190 kilometers from Five Wells Roping Rodeo Arena, TX?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.402227 30.995182)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.970102 30.345105)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.402227 30.995182)',4326)::geography, 190000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.402227 30.995182)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
